Representing the value in the form of charts is called Visualization

In pandas or datascience, Visualization can be done using below library

1. matplotlib
2. seaborn
3. plotly
4. dash

Types of Charts:

1. Uni-Variate (Single Column or Single Data)
1. Bi-Variate (Min two column needed (x and y))

Working flow:
1. Number vs Number
2. Category vs Number
3. Number only
4. Categories only

Tools for Visualisation:
1. Power BI
2. Tableau
3. Detaiku
4. Cloud (AWS and Azure)

